The paper deals with image relighting, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of material constrained layer decomposition and patch match based image warping suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper's focus on producing similar illumination effects using a single reference image may also make it relevant to the field of machine learning (cs.LG).
